                <AlertTitle>Under the Hood</AlertTitle>
                <AlertDescription>
                    The entire sidebar system is managed by the <code>RzSidebarProvider</code>, which hosts an Alpine.js component (<code>x-data="rzSidebar"</code>) to control its state and interactivity, including collapsible behavior and keyboard shortcuts.
                </AlertDescription>
            </RzAlert>

